description:
A young IFO pilot for Team Pied Piper. Fleur is the only daughter of Christophe Blanc who presides over GENERATION BLUE, the organization that commands Team Pied Piper`s activities. She is jealous of http://anidb.net/ch40360 [Ao]`s natural-born IFO piloting abilities.
Source: ANN
name: Fleur Blanc
